title: Raw Speed: Eau Rouge at the Spa 24 - /DRIVE MOMENTS
description: This should give you a good sense of some the raw speed you see at the Spa circuit in Francorchamps, Spa, Belgium. Be sure to check out another epic racing tale told through the eyes of Leo Parente in a special episode of Shakedown: next week on Tuesday afternoon we'll be bringing you our 24 Hours of Spa adventure from this years 2012 race.
